  "texts": [
    "• ReAct (Yao et al., 2023).",
    "A single agent iteratively completes the task, with each step involving the agent giving out thoughts and actions based on current observations.",
    "• P&S (Wang et al., 2023b).",
    "In this setting, the agent first creates a plan with multiple steps and then follows the ReAct pattern to solve the problem step by step.",
    "• P&E (Sun et al., 2023)."
